    "description": "<strong>COMMAND MECHS, CONQUER MARS!</strong><br><br>Space Gears是一款以火星地球化为背景的新一代即时战略游戏。 <br>由热爱科幻题材与RTS游戏的韩国开发者倾力打造。<br><br>想体验RTS游戏，但因为建造顺序、资源管理、基地扩张等因素过于复杂，所以感觉入手门槛太高吗？Space Gears可在进入战斗前提前收集资源、组建部队，使得在战斗时只需要沉浸在操作和策略之中即可。游戏中可享受各种模式的PvE和PvP战斗的双重乐趣，敬请期待。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/03830a75e32f32786fe76ae62eea52e6.poster.avif?t=1713506682\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/03830a75e32f32786fe76ae62eea52e6.webm?t=1713506682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/03830a75e32f32786fe76ae62eea52e6.mp4?t=1713506682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆ 世界观</strong><br>21世纪末，宇宙大开拓时代的序幕逐渐升起。这一时期人类的未来，正跨越月球奔向火星。<br>火星地球化计划的成败掌握在开拓者们和他们的机甲“Space Gears”手中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/77336fdb31998c4f3c5458a713d9300c.avif?t=1713506682\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br><strong>◆ Space Gears</strong><br>Space Gears是一种机甲，可以取代战斗和各种劳动。<br>在火星上有着多个机甲制造商，提供着充满特色的各种机甲。<br>你可以使用任意公司的设计图来组合自己的专属机甲。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/2cd1e999be746a3ddc4ee497e46df086.poster.avif?t=1713506682\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/2cd1e999be746a3ddc4ee497e46df086.webm?t=1713506682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/2cd1e999be746a3ddc4ee497e46df086.mp4?t=1713506682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆ 未知存在</strong><br>贫瘠的不毛之地，每时每刻变化万千的天气，还有各种怪异现象。火星中存在着无数的危险因素。<br>其中最大的危险就是感染了未知AI病毒的机甲。<br>你需要探查整个火星地区，清剿这些机甲并找到AI病毒的根源。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302770/extras/ef36309fc12b52e59541cb2c63770f1f.avif?t=1713506682\" width=616 height=250 /></span>",
